  "original_title": "\u0bb5\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0baa\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0b95\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0ba9\u0bbf\u0bae\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b86\u0bb2\u0baf \u0ba4\u0bc0\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b8e\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bc0\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc8 \u0bae\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u00a0 \u0b87\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bae\u0bcd ! \u0baa\u0bb0\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc0\u0bb5\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bc0\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc8 \u0bae\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u00a0 \u0bae\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd !",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Vattuvagal Saptha Kannimar Temple, the army blocked the road to take tirtham! Paranthan Mullaitivu Road Blocked People's Protest!",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "On the occasion of the annual festival of the historic Vattuvagal Saptha Kannimar temple of Mullaitivu district yesterday, Monday (4) at 5:30 pm, devotees went towards the Mullaitivu ocean to take tirtha from the temple.",
        "Soldiers on their way to Vattuvagal Saptha Kannimar temple in Mullaithivu district have blocked the road and set up a massive army camp. The army, which had allowed settlement till now, has banned settlement this time.",
        "There was confusion at the said place yesterday evening (04) due to the army not allowing them to go through the said road.",
        "Last year, during the corona period, when the army was not allowed to pass through this road, they used to go through an alternative road and settled on the beach. Due to that unusual action, there were many casualties in that area and it was reported as a sad event for the village. The temple administration had discussed with the army camp two months ago saying that it cannot be changed and three days ago they have given a document in writing.",
        "However, the army officials from the army camp said that the higher echelons of the army had not given permission to go through this route and the military officials from the army camp had blocked the road at the gate of the army camp and prevented them from entering.",
        "There was confusion when the people who went there requested them in various ways but they did not allow them in any way.",
        "Due to the tragedies that had already changed the regulations, they could not go that way this time and when they told them for several hours to let them go, they did not agree until 9:30. People blocked the road and protested by visiting the place where the land belonging to the Kannimar temple had been seized and the road blocked and the army was not cooperating with the temple duties.",
        "When the people came down to the streets and tried to fight, more than 50 armed soldiers were brought to a certain area and there was a tense situation for a few hours.",
        "In the background of this, after the continuous demand of the people that the army, which did not cooperate with their temple duties, should leave the temple land, the soldiers promised to remove their belongings from the land of the people in the area and immediately took the belongings from the place overnight.",
        "As the said place was freed from the army, immediately the people demarcated the said place and fenced it, which is currently involved and they have put up a sign saying that the said land belongs to Saptha Kannimar temple.",
        "At the same time, the army is trying to change the name of the road where they are going to settle as their army camp road. More than 200 people have gathered at that place and it is noteworthy that the people are still there till now, demanding that the army should leave the place completely."
      ],
